data.description: Fantastic well maintained 3 bedroom home in Franklin Township. The abundance of windows & natural light flows through every room! The vaulted ceiling in the open concept living area with fireplace is ideal for relaxing or entertaining family & friends. The kitchen includes all appliances, plus tons of cabinet & counter space. Meal prep at the center island or pull up a stool for a quick snack. Grill and dine al fresco on the outside open patio just off the kitchen. The primary bedroom is spacious with an ensuite bath. The other 2 bedrooms share a full bath & are generously sized. A utility room and 2 car garage round out the space. A ranch home of this quality is hard to find in today's market.
